From the sources
================
 * Install the dependencies ([[Requirements]]) don't forget the [eZ Components](http://ezcomponents.org/docs/install)
 * Download Gauffr
 * Install the __Gauffr__ directory in __/usr/share/php__ or equivalent (Don't forget to check [set_include_path](http://php.net/manual/function.set-include-path.php))
 * Use the install.php scripts (TODO)
 * [[ConfigureGauffr]]
 * Check if Gauffr is operational
~~~
Gauffr::info()
~~~
 * Include Gauffr and [[UseGauffr]]

From RPM
========
 * Install the dependencies ([[Requirements]]) don't forget the [eZ Components](http://ezcomponents.org/docs/install)
 * Download RPM of Gauffr
 * Use the install.php scripts (TODO)
 * [[ConfigureGauffr]] in __/etc/gauffr/__
 * Check if Gauffr is operational
~~~
Gauffr::info()
~~~
 * Include Gauffr and [[UseGauffr]]

With YUM
========
 * Use [my repository](http://www.llaumgui.com/pages/depot-llaumgui)
 * Install Gauffr
~~~
yum --enablerepo=remi install gauffr
~~~
 * Use the install.php scripts (TODO)
 * [[ConfigureGauffr]] in __/etc/gauffr/__
 * Check if Gauffr is operational
~~~
Gauffr::info()
~~~
 * Include Gauffr and [[UseGauffr]]